{
  "page": "Properties",
  "url": "https://schedule-1.fandom.com/wiki/Properties",
  "sections": [
    {
      "heading": "Introduction",
      "level": 0,
      "content": [
        {
          "text": "There are multiple available properties to obtain or purchase with cash (in some cases) or Online Balance at Ray's Realty. Some properties are free."
        },
        {
          "text": "It is worth noting that Businesses also have small, but usable buildable areas that can also be used for a small amount of storage or crafting. They do not provide any water sources or Loading Docks and can not have Employees."
        },
        {
          "text": "All Properties and Businesses have a Base Starting Temperature of 20°C, or 68°F. The Sewer Office is 10°C, or 50°F. This means Marijuana and Coca plants grow slower in the Sewer Office without an AC Unit set to Heat, but Shrooms can grow there without the AC Unit. See AC Unit for more info on Temperature."
        }
      ],
      "lists": [],
      "tables": []
    },
